Title: Do Svidaniya, Igor, and Thank You for NGINX - NGINX
Description: With profound gratitude for his contributions to both F5 and the Internet at large, we say goodbye to Igor Sysoev, author of NGINX and co-founder of NGINX, Inc., as he leaves to spend time with friends and family and work on personal projects. Спасибо, Игорь.

Title: Tricking Postgres into using an insane - but 200x faster - query plan
Description: At Spacelift, we use PostgreSQL (specifically Aurora Serverless) for most of our primary database needs. This article will show you our optimization story and how PostgreSQL row count estimation can go very wrong.
